General.Name: 29Metals Ltd
General.Description: 29Metals Limited explores, develops, and produces copper focused base and precious metals. The company explores for copper, zinc, gold, and silver deposits. It holds interest in the Golden Grove property located in Western Australia; the Capricorn Copper property situated in Queensland; and the Redhill project located in southern Chile. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is headquartered in Melbourne, Australia.
